sentence: In early trading on Wednesday, shares of Goldman Sachs Group ( GS ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.2%.
Year to date, Goldman Sachs Group has lost about 4.2% of its value.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Boeing ( BA ), trading down 1.8%.
Boeing is showing a gain of 15.8% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Procter & Gamble ( PG ), trading down 1.5%, and Wal-Mart Stores ( WMT ), trading up 0.7% on the day.
